               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18481127-name-314" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18481127-name-314" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481127-name-314" type="surname" value="BURTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481127-name-314" type="given" value="JOSHUA"></interp>JOSHUA BURTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Great Turnstile. On 16th Nov., the prisoner came and asked for a pie—it came to 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—he gave me a shilling—I gave him change—he went away—I found the shilling was bad, marked it, and kept it apart from other coin—on 20th Nov. the prisoner came for another article—he paid me a shilling, I saw it was bad, and said, "How many more are you going to bring me of this kind"—he said he did not know it was bad—I gave him into custody—I gave the policeman the two shillings.</p>
